@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_eskpbw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((0.17 / (v2 + 0.13 + v2 + 0.37)) / v2)
    v0 = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.76) * (v2 + 0.70 - v2 + 0.18)) - (wp.cos(v1 + 0.96) + (v2 + 0.92 - v0 + 0.28)))
    v0 = v1
    tmp = 0.05
    data[tid] = v0
